        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">This exchange is an aggregate of proxies for applied pesticide(s) Pydiflumetofen, Flumiclorac-Pentyl (3.138E-3 kg/ha {1,2,1,1,1}; 3.094E-3 kg/ha {1,2,1,1,1}, respectively).
