Heuzé V., Tran G., Lebas F. (2017) Maize grain. Feedipedia, a programme by INRAE, CIRAD, AFZ and FAO. https://www.feedipedia.org/node/556 Last updated on September 7, 2017, 14:29. .  
USDA NASS (2021) SOYBEAN, AT HARVEST, GRAIN - MOISTURE, 5 YEAR AVG, MEASURED IN PCT. US Department of Agriculture (USDA). https://quickstats.nass.usda.gov (direct query: https://quickstats.nass.usda.gov/results/13FC0C89-E211-3D0B-A9C5-BCFC35728512)</comment>
